data.description: Priced to sell! *Seller offers 2-1 Rate Buy Down, which will lower your interest rates in the first 2 years! (Or $ 12,000 as closing cost credit instead)* Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence nestled in South Tampa. As you step inside, you'll enter the separate dining room, adorned with new blinds, providing an elegant setting for Holiday meals, or casual dinner times. The interior walls and doors have been tastefully enhanced with a FRESH coat of paint and the owner added brand-NEW carpet to the stairs and entire second floor.    The heart of this home is its spacious open kitchen equipped with modern appliances and ample counter space, it's a perfect hub for entertaining, while your guests enjoys the sizable open concept living room.     The primary bedroom, with its elegant tray ceiling, offers a spacious walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom with shower, separate bath tub and enclosed toilet. The bath tubs, showers and sinks are re-caulked throughout the home for the new owner’s convenience, and all toilets have new seats installed. Two out of the four bedrooms boast walk-in closets, providing ample storage for your wardrobe and personal belongings. The well-designed layout ensures that each bedroom offers a retreat-like feel, making this home a sanctuary for its residents.    The allure of this property extends beyond the interior. A fully fenced-in yard offers privacy and a comfortable space for outdoor activities. The corner lot location ensures a sense of openness. Conveniently located just minutes from MacDill Air Force Base and with easy access to local stores, restaurants and highways. Whether you're seeking a tranquil space to call home or a place to entertain, this charming residence is fully ready to welcome you in. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your dream home! – Located in flood zone X with no flood insurance required. Check out the video/Virtual Tour!
